							<div class="blogpost-title">
								<a href="../understanding-treatment-options-for-ischemic-stroke">
									Understanding the Best Treatment Options for Ischemic Stroke
								</a>
							</div>
															<div class="blogpost-thumbnail">
									<div class="bg-thumb" style="background-image: url(../../files/b9a6c0bd951910dac160fc672128fda58c00fdb0.jpg);"></div>
								</div>
														<div class="source">
															</div>
							<div class="blogpost-content">
								<p><span style="color: rgb(112, 87, 75); font-size: 16px;">Millions of Americans take medicines for many different health conditions. Many do not understand the seriousness of the health conditions being treated or the importance of the medicines that have been prescribed. This lack of understanding about health conditions is called medical illiteracy and is a significant contributor to noncompliance â€“ or people failing to take their medicines and incorporate diet and lifestyle changes as prescribed by their healthcare providers.</span><br></p>
